name: Chris Crawford
review: The people are very friendly, kind and good spirited. Had a great time setting up and running the rock wall for these people and would be glad to do it agian.

name: Michael G
review: Christ centered and biblical, the Word is preached faithfully. Expositional preaching verse by verse! Soli Deo gloria!

name: Bill Buell
review: Great place to worship and great people.
